<SceneText>
  <FriendlyName>Chapter 5 (Tytree) - End</FriendlyName>
  <Speakers>
    <Section>Speaker</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ヴェイグ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Veigue</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>12</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ティトレイ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Tytree</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>13</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Speakers>
  <Strings>
    <Section>Main Text</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>お前はもう少し周りを見るべきだ。
その上で、自分の為すべき事をしろ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You need to pay more attention to what's
going on around you. You can do what
you feel needs to be done after that.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>12</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>わかったよ。
たしかにおれは
すぐに周りが見えなくなっちまうからな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I gotcha.
It's true I lose sight of what's around me pretty fast.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>13</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>気をつける事にするぜ！
ありがとな、ヴェイグ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I'll be careful! Thanks, Veigue!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>13</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>……わかればいいんだ。
なら、あとはお前一人で……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...That's good, then. In which case,
you can handle it on your own from here on.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>12</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>そう言うなって。
とびきりうまいピーチパイ
おごり続けてやるからさ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Don't say that. I'll keep treating you to
the greatest peach pie you've ever had.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>13</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>どこまでもいくぞ、ティトレイ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I'll go anywhere, Tytree.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>12</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>おうよ！
世の中には
まだまだ更生させなきゃなんねぇ奴がいる</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Yeah! There are still folks out there
who I gotta set on the right path.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>13</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>おれ達の戦いは、まだ始まったばかりだぜ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Our battle has only just begun!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>13</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
  <Strings>
    <Section>Unreferenced</Section>
